694
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:24,040
Indeed, Mr. Zhuang Bi.

695
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:27,180
So invitations aren’t necessary.

696
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:29,770
The uninvited go that way.

697
00:40:29,770 --> 00:40:32,020
Are the guests divided into two groups?

698
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:34,540
Maybe they’re seated separately.

699
00:40:35,090 --> 00:40:37,050
Are there two sessions?

700
00:40:37,050 --> 00:40:38,790
One for each group?

701
00:40:39,810 --> 00:40:41,660
(Huo’s Manor)
The waterside pavilion isn’t big enough.

702
00:40:41,660 --> 00:40:42,570
As per Lord’s order,

703
00:40:42,570 --> 00:40:44,700
the uninvited go this way, please.

704
00:40:44,700 --> 00:40:47,090
Your seats are over there.

705
00:40:47,940 --> 00:40:48,630
Fine.

706
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:50,290
I’ll

707
00:40:50,290 --> 00:40:51,850
see you later.

708
00:40:59,290 --> 00:41:02,700
Guests are separated by invitations?

709
00:41:03,220 --> 00:41:04,900
Miss Zhou, Mr. Xie,

710
00:41:05,330 --> 00:41:08,420
we can go together.

711
00:41:09,330 --> 00:41:10,260
No, thanks.

712
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:12,260
My cousins should be over there.

713
00:41:12,260 --> 00:41:13,940
We’ll join them.

714
00:41:15,130 --> 00:41:16,500
Thank you, Mr. Zhu.

715
00:41:16,500 --> 00:41:17,660
Thank you.

716
00:41:20,740 --> 00:41:21,810
Please.

717
00:41:24,940 --> 00:41:26,020
Let’s go.

718
00:41:37,220 --> 00:41:39,570
What is Huo Liantao up to?

719
00:41:40,090 --> 00:41:41,260
Be quiet.

720
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:42,100
I’m memorizing the direction.

721
00:41:43,290 --> 00:41:44,570
This forest

722
00:41:44,570 --> 00:41:45,550
is a maze.

723
00:41:46,260 --> 00:41:48,300
It’s hard to get out once we’re in.

724
00:42:03,660 --> 00:42:06,370
Don’t you think something is odd?

725
00:42:06,370 --> 00:42:07,370
Odd?

726
00:42:10,900 --> 00:42:13,220
These trees look fine to me.

727
00:42:13,220 --> 00:42:13,810
How are they odd?

728
00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:14,940
I mean,

729
00:42:15,610 --> 00:42:16,960
isn’t this place...

730
00:42:29,610 --> 00:42:30,770
Over there.

731
00:42:31,370 --> 00:42:32,100
Li Yan.

732
00:42:34,050 --> 00:42:35,210
What are you doing?

733
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:37,530
There might be a snake.

734
00:42:37,530 --> 00:42:38,740
Snake!

735
00:42:38,740 --> 00:42:39,720
Where is it?

736
