747
00:43:11,090 --> 00:43:12,370
What is he doing here?

748
00:43:12,700 --> 00:43:14,050
Who is it?

749
00:43:14,050 --> 00:43:16,500
He seems to be
that Poisoner with Mr. Xie.

750
00:43:17,220 --> 00:43:18,420
How dare you

751
00:43:18,420 --> 00:43:20,700
release a snake!

752
00:43:20,700 --> 00:43:21,180
I did that

753
00:43:21,180 --> 00:43:23,360
to punish Ding Kui
for bullying a waitress.

754
00:43:24,020 --> 00:43:26,130
It’s the master’s order

755
00:43:26,130 --> 00:43:27,500
to separate the invited
and uninvited guests.

756
00:43:27,500 --> 00:43:29,450
Go to him if you have a problem with it.

757
00:43:29,980 --> 00:43:31,700
Why bully a girl?

758
00:43:31,700 --> 00:43:33,700
You’re playing the hero.

759
00:43:33,700 --> 00:43:35,810
Let’s see

760
00:43:35,810 --> 00:43:36,980
how tough you are!

761
00:43:51,770 --> 00:43:53,180
Who are you?

762
00:43:53,530 --> 00:43:56,090
Yang Jin from the Cloud Ravine.

763
00:43:56,090 --> 00:43:57,530
And me,

764
00:43:58,020 --> 00:44:00,090
Li Yan from the Fortress
of the Forty-Eight.

765
00:44:00,460 --> 00:44:01,810
Wait for it.

766
00:44:01,810 --> 00:44:03,260
This isn’t over!

767
00:44:03,530 --> 00:44:05,570
I’ll report to Tortoise Master

768
00:44:05,570 --> 00:44:06,850
to teach you a lesson.

769
00:44:07,220 --> 00:44:08,020
Let’s go.

770
00:44:12,050 --> 00:44:14,810
I learned that move from your cousin.

771
00:44:14,810 --> 00:44:15,770
Didn’t I do it faster

772
00:44:15,770 --> 00:44:16,850
and better than her?

773
00:44:16,850 --> 00:44:18,420
How are your hands?

774
00:44:18,420 --> 00:44:20,500
Am I more skilled than her?

775
00:44:21,260 --> 00:44:22,900
Thanks for your help.

776
00:44:26,220 --> 00:44:27,700
Step back, please. Thanks.

777
00:44:30,770 --> 00:44:31,900
Are you from the Small Medicine Valley?

778
00:44:31,900 --> 00:44:32,730
Yes.

779
00:44:33,530 --> 00:44:36,020
But he knows nothing about medicine.

780
00:44:36,020 --> 00:44:37,770
