782
00:44:42,740 --> 00:44:44,460
attack them with your snakes?

783
00:44:44,460 --> 00:44:45,940
My snakes?

784
00:44:45,940 --> 00:44:47,980
They’re my babies

785
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:49,260
and worth much more

786
00:44:49,260 --> 00:44:51,020
than their lives.

787
00:44:55,090 --> 00:44:56,080
