00:45:19,420 --> 00:45:20,500
Hongyu.

800
00:45:20,770 --> 00:45:23,130
Hongyu. Hongyu.

801
00:45:23,660 --> 00:45:26,020
We’ve already saved him.

802
00:45:26,020 --> 00:45:27,850
Why help him find his snake?

803
00:45:28,940 --> 00:45:30,020
Hey,

804
00:45:30,020 --> 00:45:31,700
is a big man like you

805
00:45:31,700 --> 00:45:33,530
afraid of snakes?

806
00:45:33,530 --> 00:45:34,940
I’m not. I...

807
00:45:38,130 --> 00:45:39,490
What is that?

808
00:45:41,500 --> 00:45:43,420
I raised those snakes.

809
00:45:43,420 --> 00:45:45,220
They can recognize
the sound of my flute.

810
00:45:45,220 --> 00:45:46,740
But right after

811
00:45:46,740 --> 00:45:48,130
entering in the woods,

812
00:45:48,130 --> 00:45:49,810
they ran wild

813
00:45:49,810 --> 00:45:50,920
as if something scared them.

814
00:46:02,890 --> 00:46:06,400
